Subject: [PATCH 1/5] wined3d: Use UBO for vertex shader float constants if
 supported.

Signed-off-by: Paul Gofman <gofmanp@gmail.com>
---
 dlls/wined3d/adapter_gl.c      |   3 +
 dlls/wined3d/glsl_shader.c     | 113 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++----
